General.Name: Qleanair Holding AB
General.Description: QleanAir AB (publ) provides air cleaning solutions for professional and public indoor environments in Sweden and internationally. The company offers freestanding smoking cabins for protection against secondhand smoke; cleanrooms for aseptic spaces; and smoking solutions for shopping malls and casinos, as well as offshore facilities, such as oil platforms, offshore, cruise ships and shipping, and security facilities and institutions. It serves production, logistics and warehouses, food and beverage, healthcare, transportation, and airport industries; and MedTech companies and compounding pharmacies, as well as offices, conference centers, hotels, restaurants, and school facilities. The company was formerly known as QleanAir Holding AB (publ) and changed its name to QleanAir AB (publ) in July 2021. QleanAir AB (publ) was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Solna, Sweden.
